ith now?"],[4137,4525,"You must be really good at pleasing men"],[4546,4821,"to shop in a store like this."],[4821,5038,"He is not some old man."],[5096,5242,"He is much more handsome"],[5242,5463,"than the clown standing next to you."],[5505,5584,"You!"],[5605,5772,"Don't worry, babe."],[5880,6047,"She's probably just jealous."],[6131,6222,"In fact,"],[6256,6473,"I think she came here just to see me."],[6485,6706,"Oh, that's nonsense."],[7069,7236,"Did the last lesson"],[7236,7482,"I gave you not properly teach you?"],[7557,7745,"Still clinging to this city,"],[7745,7874,"refusing to leave,"],[7874,8103,"and now trying to steal my man?"],[8124,8337,"Claudia, I didn't steal your man."],[8337,8579,"And I would never even want him."],[8750,8938,"If you like this store so much,"],[9004,9205,"you can have it. I'll leave."]],"31":[[183,442,"I hate it when people touch what's mine."],[462,650,"Claudia I already gave you the store."],[650,817,"What more do you want?"],[955,1063,"Giving it to me?"],[1088,1418,"Oh please, who do you think you are?"],[1459,1605,"I'm the daughter of the richest"],[1605,1755,"man in the state."],[1760,1901,"What could you possibly give to me"],[1901,2077,"that I don't already have?"],[2143,2277,"Go teach her a lesson."],[2323,2523,"She's pregnant, isn't she?"],[2590,2748,"Make her lose that baby."],[2748,2902,"Let's see if that man"],[2902,3103,"still spends money on you now."],[3123,3224,"Don't worry, babe."],[3286,3420,"I won't hold back."],[4245,4391,"Oh Anastasia."],[4446,4612,"No matter who you hook up with,"],[4646,4788,"they will never"],[4808,5004,"be as powerful as Claudia."],[5092,5171,"Today."],[5276,5417,"You're in your place."],[5497,5643,"Let me go!"],[5647,5818,"You can scream all you want,"],[5955,6181,"no one will save you."],[6218,6498,"No, this baby is a miracle to kayden."],[6498,6598,"It can't be harmed."]],"32":[[41,154,"Oh."],[154,287,"Are you okay?"],[316,433,"I'm fine."],[529,658,"Just don't let her get away."],[696,788